        <h1>Consumer Duty for Motor Dealers: A Practical Guide to FCA Expectations</h1>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Consumer Duty is one of the most significant regulatory developments affecting FCA-authorised motor dealers.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Introduced by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA), Consumer Duty places a greater focus on customer outcomes and requires firms to consider how customers experience products and services throughout the customer journey.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">For motor dealers, Consumer Duty is particularly relevant where vehicle finance, credit broking activities and regulated consumer credit services are provided.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Understanding Consumer Duty is important because it influences how dealerships communicate with customers, explain finance products, support vulnerable customers, monitor outcomes and demonstrate compliance.</p>
        <div class="ccr009-actions">
          <a class="ccr009-btn ccr009-btn--primary" href="/contact#send-message">Get Consumer Duty Support</a>
          <a class="ccr009-btn ccr009-btn--secondary" href="/motor-dealer-compliance">View Motor Dealer Compliance Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
